code: SELECT DISTINCT flight_1.flight_id FROM flight flight_1 , airport_service airport_service_1 , city city_1 , airport_service airport_service_2 , city city_2 , flight_fare flight_fare_1 , fare fare_1 , fare_basis fare_basis_1 WHERE flight_1.from_airport = airport_service_1.airport_code AND airport_service_1.city_code = city_1.city_code AND city_1.city_name = CITYNAME_0 AND ( flight_1.to_airport = airport_service_2.airport_code AND airport_service_2.city_code = city_2.city_code AND city_2.city_name = CITYNAME_1 AND flight_1.flight_id = flight_fare_1.flight_id AND flight_fare_1.fare_id = fare_1.fare_id AND fare_1.round_trip_cost IS NOT NULL AND ( fare_1.fare_basis_code = fare_basis_1.fare_basis_code AND fare_basis_1.class_type = CLASSTYPE_0 AND 1 = 1 ) )
